Almost everyone has played some kind of shoot-em-up game, but did you ever think about how the player’s plane could upgrade it’s weapon? This Invader game could tell you the secret.<br>Weapon towers floating in the Universe, if a power source attached it, it would become to an active weapon, shooting at opponents. If it lost the power source, it will be floating again.<br><br>LÖVE 0.7.1 is needed to play this game.<dl class="file"><dt><img src="./images/upload_icons/love.png" alt="" /> <a class="postlink" href="http://love2d.org/forums/download/file.php?id=2513">InvaderGame.love</a></dt></dl><br /><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><a href="http://love2d.org/forums/download/file.php?id=2512&amp;mode=view"><img src="http://love2d.org/forums/download/file.php?id=2512" class="postimage" alt="03_fight2.png" /></a></dt></dl><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://love2d.org/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1666">hengying</a> — Thu Apr 14, 2011 1:00 pm</p><hr />
